@startuml
title 13. Sub-Agent Task State Machine (ProcessStatus)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<Terminal>> #FADBD8
  BackgroundColor<<Active>> #E8F8F5
}

[*] --> ACCEPTED : Request Received (UseCase)

state "ACCEPTED" as ACCEPTED : Task enqueued in Redis
state "RUNNING" as RUNNING <<Active>> : Worker processing task

ACCEPTED --> RUNNING : Worker dequeues (AgentExecutor.execute)

state RUNNING {
  [*] --> Planning
  Planning --> Executing : Tool Plan created
  Executing --> Planning : Tool result processed
  Executing --> Composing : All tools completed
  Planning --> Composing : No tools needed
}

RUNNING --> COMPLETED : Final Answer generated
RUNNING --> FAILED : Exception caught

state "COMPLETED" as COMPLETED <<Terminal>>
state "FAILED" as FAILED <<Terminal>>

COMPLETED --> [*]
FAILED --> [*]

note bottom
  - 상태 전이는 AgentPersistence를 통해 Redis에 영속화된다.
  - 모든 상태 변화는 AgentProgressPublisher를 통해 클라이언트에 스트리밍된다.
end note
@enduml
